301
00:24:41,764 --> 00:24:45,184
That's what I'd call cruel
and unusual punishment.

302
00:24:45,267 --> 00:24:47,353
Yeah. No question.

303
00:24:47,436 --> 00:24:51,482
Guess they figure by the time they get
around to killin' you, you'll be grateful.

304
00:24:51,565 --> 00:24:55,360
Well, I'm just glad you consider me
a notch up from that kind of torture.

305
00:24:55,444 --> 00:24:57,404
Just a notch.

306
00:24:59,448 --> 00:25:02,242
What do you want?

307
00:25:02,325 --> 00:25:04,661
Well, let's start with
