333
00:26:44,883 --> 00:26:48,052
Oh. Well, sorry I asked.

334
00:26:48,136 --> 00:26:50,972
It say in my file
I take drawing lessons?

335
00:26:51,055 --> 00:26:53,599
- No, I don't think so.
- I do.

336
00:26:53,683 --> 00:26:58,020
Through the mail.
Helps me pass the time.

337
00:26:58,104 --> 00:27:00,815
You know, and every week they
give you something new to draw.

338
00:27:00,898 --> 00:27:02,858
This week it's castles.

339
