00:29:35,714 --> 00:29:38,258
- Can you tell me where Morris lives?
- Next one.

381
00:29:51,104 --> 00:29:53,773
Hi.

382
00:29:53,857 --> 00:29:55,775
- Who are you?
- Uh, Miss Morris, well, I'm Rick Hayes.

383
00:29:55,859 --> 00:29:57,777
