- How'd you track him down there?

952
01:09:48,625 --> 01:09:52,546
Well, Sam...
Sam says good luck.

953
01:09:52,671 --> 01:09:55,132
- Tell Sam thank you.
- You're welcome, Rick. Bye.

954
01:10:07,143 --> 01:10:09,604
You won't be able
to take those.

955
01:10:09,729 --> 01:10:13,399
- Why not?
