969
01:14:22,848 --> 01:14:25,851
That's okay too.

970
01:14:25,976 --> 01:14:29,897
We will need for you to change
into that blue uniform there.

971
01:14:32,190 --> 01:14:34,568
Cindy, I'm on 24-hour call.

972
01:14:34,651 --> 01:14:37,988
I'll come to you
whenever you want.

973
01:14:38,071 --> 01:14:42,075
Okay. Well...

974
01:14:42,158 --> 01:14:45,745
we're going to try to make you
as comfortable as possible.

975
01:14:45,870 --> 01:14:48,248
Thanks.

976
01:15:41,174 --> 01:15:44,260
Okay, c'mon. Let's go.

977
01:15:45,803 --> 01:15:48,097
Get your ass outta the car.

978
01:15:49,432 --> 01:15:52,309
They go to the beach
every weekend.

979
01:16:08,742 --> 01:16:12,078
- They got a V.C.R.
