980
01:16:39,480 --> 01:16:41,690
Shit!

981
01:16:43,108 --> 01:16:45,861
Oh, it's you, you fuckin' whore.

982
01:16:45,945 --> 01:16:48,322
Get outta my house.
Get outta my house!

983
01:16:48,447 --> 01:16:52,201
Get outta here, you thievin' whore!
Get outta my house!

984
01:17:18,184 --> 01:17:20,728
There it is.

985
01:18:04,270 --> 01:18:06,898
Judge Gorman!

986
01:18:06,981 --> 01:18:09,984
Goddam it, Will! What the hell
are you doin' here anyway?

987
01:18:10,109 --> 01:18:11,819
- Judge Gorman?
- Yes.

988
01:18:11,902 --> 01:18:14,447
Your Honour, I'm sorry.
My name is Rick Hayes...

989
01:18:14,572 --> 01:18:18,409
and I have a motion from State Legal Aid
