994
01:18:34,091 --> 01:18:36,801
I'll radio my ruling back
from the ranger station.

995
01:18:36,885 --> 01:18:39,429
Thank you, sir.
All right.

996
01:18:39,554 --> 01:18:41,765
Thank you.

