998
01:18:48,688 --> 01:18:51,232
prison officials continue
preparations for the execution...

999
01:18:51,315 --> 01:18:53,443
of double-murderer Cindy Liggett.

1000
01:18:53,568 --> 01:18:57,613
Unless a stay is issued, Liggett is
scheduled to die in less than 24 hours.

1001
01:19:22,345 --> 01:19:26,433
I found that judge.
I think he might help us.

1002
01:19:42,823 --> 01:19:45,618
- You gonna stay?
- Yeah.

1003
01:19:47,411 --> 01:19:50,122
To the end?

1004
01:19:53,375 --> 01:19:55,419
When I go,
will you be there?

1005
01:19:59,506 --> 01:20:02,301
It's too much to ask, huh?

1006
01:20:02,384 --> 01:20:04,845
No.

1007
01:20:06,555 --> 01:20:09,724
If it happens, I will be there.

1008
01:21:00,815 --> 01:21:02,942
I'm not a real breakfast person.

1009
01:21:03,026 --> 01:21:06,446
Yeah, I'm just a...
I'm a coffee man myself.

1010
01:21:06,571 --> 01:21:08,781
Me too.

1011
01:21:29,885 --> 01:21:35,307
You see arriving here today some
who are for capital punishment
while others are against it.

1012
01:21:35,432 --> 01:21:39,353
Others are carrying placards
saying "Cindy must die."

1013
01:21:39,478 --> 01:21:42,481
- Kill the bitch.
- Others saying, "Thou shalt not kill."

1014
01:22:00,331 --> 01:22:02,291
She know I'm comin'?

1015
01:22:02,375 --> 01:22:05,336
Well, she's gonna be
glad to see ya.

1016
01:22:16,597 --> 01:22:18,474
Bill?

1017
01:22:21,518 --> 01:22:23,395
Bill.

1018
01:22:25,355 --> 01:22:27,149
Hey.

1019
01:22:27,274 --> 01:22:31,027
- I'm sorry.
- I know.

1020
01:22:31,111 --> 01:22:35,407
I know, but what
you did was right.

1021
01:22:35,490 --> 01:22:39,077
I didn't know this would happen.
If I'd known...

1022
01:22:39,160 --> 01:22:42,664
