1036
01:23:32,420 --> 01:23:35,339
All right. What are we gonna do
if he turns us down?

1037
01:23:35,423 --> 01:23:37,717
Only place left is
the U.S. Supreme Court.

1038
01:23:37,800 --> 01:23:40,344
- Well, is there time?
- Not really.

1039
01:23:40,428 --> 01:23:43,931
