1040
01:23:44,056 --> 01:23:48,519
Well, then... then he just better come
through and that damn radio
better work.

1041
01:23:48,602 --> 01:23:52,523
- I hope so.
- Well, do it.

1042
01:23:52,648 --> 01:23:57,027
- All right.
- All right or yes? Look at me.

1043
01:23:57,152 --> 01:24:02,991
You better look me in the eye and say yes,
'cause I'll be watchin' you.

1044
01:24:03,116 --> 01:24:07,829
