1046
01:24:23,553 --> 01:24:26,097
I mean, we don't pick up
that goddam signal, she's dead.

1047
01:24:26,222 --> 01:24:28,933
Listen, Rick, we've still got
some time. Don't give up.

1048
01:24:29,016 --> 01:24:31,143
Aw, Linda, he's gotta
