right before they kill ya.

1057
01:25:58,770 --> 01:26:01,063
Hello, Cindy.

1058
01:26:02,732 --> 01:26:05,192
How's that steak?

1059
01:26:05,317 --> 01:26:07,778
Fine... what I had of it.

1060
01:26:10,072 --> 01:26:13,909
Cindy, if you want me,
remember I'm just down the hall.

1061
01:26:13,993 --> 01:26:18,705
