1063
01:26:24,920 --> 01:26:27,589
They thought
you should have 'em.

1064
01:26:34,137 --> 01:26:36,431
Thank you.

1065
01:27:02,456 --> 01:27:04,750
Miss Liggett?

1066
01:27:04,875 --> 01:27:08,629
Dr Forrester would like
