1089
01:32:51,292 --> 01:32:54,129
Yes?

1090
01:32:56,923 --> 01:32:59,801
Yes. Stand down.
Stand down!

1091
01:33:30,205 --> 01:33:32,499
- Calm down. Calm down. It's over! It's over.
