1092
01:33:32,624 --> 01:33:36,670
- You've been saved. It's over.
- Stop it! No!

1093
01:33:36,753 --> 01:33:39,214
Cindy. Cindy.

1094
01:33:39,297 --> 01:33:42,383
You're saved. You're saved.
It's over. It's over.

1095
01:33:42,467 --> 01:33:45,470
It's over. It's okay.

1096
01:33:45,553 --> 01:33:50,016
Shh. It's okay.
It's okay. It's okay.

1097
01:33:50,099 --> 01:33:52,560
In a surprise announcement,
Deputy Warden Marvin Heinrich...

1098
01:33:52,643 --> 01:33:56,397
